\newlabel{tab:base_learners}{{10}{59}{Individual Base Learner Performance on Cross-Validated Holdout Set. The ensemble integrates four diverse base models through stacked generalization. Performance metrics are computed on temporally-held-out folds ($n=630$ observations across 5 folds). Meta Learner represents the weighted combination using estimated meta-weights}{table.caption.24}{}}
