\newlabel{tab:cv_stability}{{11}{59}{Fold-Wise Cross-Validation Performance: Coefficient of Determination ($R^2$). Five-fold temporal cross-validation on panel data respects within-entity temporal ordering. Fold stability indicates robustness of meta-weights across time windows}{table.caption.25}{}}
