\newlabel{tab:holdout_performance}{{13}{62}{Super Learner Out-of-Sample Test Set Performance. Metrics are computed on the temporally-held-out test set (holdout split: $\approx 20\%$ of data, $n \approx 150$ observations). This gold-standard evaluation set was never seen during base model training, meta-weight estimation, or any hyperparameter tuning}{table.caption.30}{}}
